headline: Startups from Australia, India and UAE crowned winners in L'Oréal Groupe's biggest Beauty Tech competition across South Asia Pacific, Middle East and North Africa
summary: Four startups from Australia, India and United Arab Emirates (UAE) have been crowned winners of L'Oréal's 2025 SAPMENA Big Bang Beauty Tech Innovation Program, the biggest open innovation competition of its kind in the South Asia Pacific, Middle East and North Africa (SAPMENA) region.
